       <div class="post-7714 page type-page status-publish has-post-thumbnail hentry" id="post-7714">
        <h2 class="entry-title">
         Home
        </h2>
        <div class="entry-content">
         <h1 style="text-align: center;">
          <strong>
           TIME FOR
           <span style="color: #ff0000;">
            ANOTHER
           </span>
           COVER REVEAL
          </strong>
         </h1>
         <h1 style="text-align: center;">
          <strong>
           Many Readers Weighed in
          </strong>
         </h1>
         <h2 style="text-align: center;">
          <strong>
           On Choosing a Cover Model for my
           <span style="color: #ff0000;">
            UPCOMING LATE JUNE
           </span>
           book
          </strong>
         </h2>
         <h1 style="text-align: center;">
          <strong>
           <em>
            SPRING’S STORM
           </em>
           .
          </strong>
         </h1>
         <h2 style="text-align: center;">
          <strong>
           AND here it is!
          </strong>
         </h2>
         <h2 style="text-align: center;">
          <strong>
           If you’d like to learn more,
           <a href="https://booksbylyncote.com/SWBS/uncategorized/another-new-cover ?">
            click here
           </a>
          </strong>
         </h2>
         <p>
          <img alt="Spring's Storm" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-8511" height="960" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" src="https://booksbylyncote.com/SWBS/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Summers-Storm-683x1024.jpg" srcset="https://booksbylyncote.com/SWBS/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Summers-Storm-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://booksbylyncote.com/SWBS/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Summers-Storm-200x300.jpg 200w, https://booksbylyncote.com/SWBS/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Summers-Storm-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://booksbylyncote.com/SWBS/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Summers-Storm-533x800.jpg 533w, https://booksbylyncote.com/SWBS/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Summers-Storm-267x400.jpg 267w, https://booksbylyncote.com/SWBS/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Summers-Storm-980x1470.jpg 980w, https://booksbylyncote.com/SWBS/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Summers-Storm.jpg 1600w" width="640"/>
         </p>
         <p>
         </p>
         <p>
